ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Audiovisual Coproduction Treaty between the Government of Canada and the Swiss Federal Council
PrecisOrder authorizing (1) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AUDIOVISUAL COPRODUCTION TREATY BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE SWISS FEDERAL COUNCIL; or (2) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers, authorizing the individuals mentioned in the order, to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the Treaty.
